room_title: Escape room "Defcon 1" by Cipher Seeker Room Escape Challenge in New York
room_description: Your team has been selected for a special mission for the US Intelligence. The task is to enter an abandoned missile bunker where a rogue computer system is attempting to lock in a launch code. In an hour the code will be complete and the missiles could destroy nearly half of the planet. Can you shut down the system in time and save the world?
